      "date": "2012-06-19 03:06:56.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.2/x86_64, CentOS release 5.8/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/a00047c6-b9b9-11e1-92fd-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
