          "date": "2012-06-18 20:04:27.000000000",
          "tz": -360
        },
        "subject": "LU-1440 tests: restore remount-ro flag to local.sh",
        "message": "LU-1440 tests: restore remount-ro flag to local.sh\n\nThe remount-ro flag was removed from the --mkfsoptions supplied for\nthe MDT, and this caused a warning from mkfs.lustre.  However, this\nisn't necessarily a valid fix for this issue.  It would be better if\nmkfs_lustre.c always added errors=remount-ro to the specified options\nif no other errors={panic,continue} flag was given.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I89c21258c74f5abcb71c4d0446f0e9cf918cfc70\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
